metadata.name: The Barbershop
metadata.description:
Title: The Barbershop

Artist: Kelsey Smith

Editions: 10,000

Medium: 120 Film

The Barbershop is a *FREE* 10,000 edition piece made as a way to give everyone the opportunity to collect a piece of Kelsey Smith's film photography work.

You can view more of Kelsey's work (including 1/1's and more editions) on the "social links" tab on his website:  
https://kelseysmith.photography/
